# Cloudflare Pages — custom headers.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/

# Block indexing for ALL pages and assets on pirxey.tech.
# pirxey.tech is a staging/experimental subdomain; content will migrate
# to pirxey.com (the canonical destination). X-Robots-Tag at HTTP layer
# covers HTML, PDFs, images, and any other crawlable resource — stronger
# than <meta robots> alone (which only works inside HTML).
/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
